## Chapter 6 The Root Causes of Failed Product Efforts

* Everything starts with ideas -> biz case -> roadmap -> requirements -> design -> build -> test -> deploy. Very waterfally.
* Business will claim to be agile but the process above is very much waterfall.
* 1. Source of ideas, they are not coming from the product team, you're not asking for a problem to be solved but for a solution to be built.
* 2. Business case revolves around "how much money you will make?" and "how much it will cost?" at the early stage of product development you cannot possibly know either of these.
* 
